data.description: This charming 2-bedroom, 1-bath starter home with a separate game room can also be used as a 3rd-bedroom - boasts original hardwood floors throughout, tile floors in bathroom, a walk-in shower with wall tile up to the ceiling. Central air and heat, a kitchen with gas cooking, solid counter tops, lots of cabinet storage with a fresh makeover and fixtures, and a security system. Additional features include a utility room with w/d connections, long driveway with a black iron gate to the covered carport, single-car detached garage, and a spacious fenced rear yard. Conveniently located near shopping, downtown, and I-35. This home is perfect for those seeking comfort and style with the opportunity to move in quickly and enjoy the delightful features of this property. **OWNER FINANCING IS AVAILALBE WITH A MIN OF 10% DOWN.** Act fast - this gem won't last long on the market!
